You seem to have both dev packages and have mixed all libraries of
both packages together as it seems.

All you need to do is adding 'stormmesa_ppc.lib' to the project
(as you have already done) plus the standard libs which are always
included. The stubs for GLUT are included in stormmesa_ppc.lib.
The actual implementation of GL, GLU and GLUT are shared libraries,
which are in LIBS: (aglppc.library, algluppc.library, aglutppc.library).

And furthermore, make sure to select the 'indirect data' model in
the compiler menu. As far as I remember there is no support for
small data model and StormMesa currently available.

